text: The Latvia women's national under-18 and under-19 is a national basketball team of Latvia and is governed by the Latvia Basketball Association. It represents Latvia in international under-19 and under-18 (under age 19 and under age 18) women's basketball competitions. ==See also== * Latvia women's national basketball team * Latvia women's national under-17 basketball team * Latvia men's national under-19 basketball team ==References== Category:Basketball in Latvia Category:Basketball teams in Latvia Category:Women's national under-19 basketball teams B
title: Latvia women's national under-19 basketball team
